 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉屌</blockquote><br />\n正常係搵野夾出黎<br />\n但個醫生睇唔到有野 <br />\n先要由鼻入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1610a3c377c0c6beee83556034e0aa4f1e3c7e","tid":323552,"uid":127605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:28:57.000Z","msg":"無耐前試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n卡住嗰刻超唔自在 瘋狂吞飯 點知都係勁痛 feel到條刺好似一直插住喉嚨咁 叫埋屋企人幫手用電筒照 都搵唔到條刺<br />\n<br />\n到第二日忍唔到 去睇醫生先知 純粹插損咗喉嚨 條刺原來一早吞咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2d91ab602a04c39825a11e6bd82c3e944c1dde","tid":323552,"uid":59550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:34:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無耐前試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n卡住嗰刻超唔自在 瘋狂吞飯 點知都係勁痛 feel到條刺好似一直插住喉嚨咁 叫埋屋企人幫手用電筒照 都搵唔到條刺<br />\n<br />\n到第二日忍唔到 去睇醫生先知 純粹插損咗喉嚨 條刺原來一早吞咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有諗過係咪我扣喉嘔到整損個喉嚨先會覺得有野係入面，所以諗住第二日睇下點先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ed7a65b0d38f5d94150b9ea77984325a485f0d","tid":323552,"uid":59550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:34:30.000Z