 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba60c8744130471a734564467d00f188c4bf68d","tid":323552,"uid":59550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/014705_a22734da0c11a16ddd2191355332ad23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F014705_a22734da0c11a16ddd2191355332ad23.jpg&h=a726a0ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n諗住啪落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 結果都無咩用仲紅咗"},{"pid":"2298a5bd8049a298bb7bc484ce8abac45347f5c9","tid":323552,"uid":127605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:48:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無耐前試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n卡住嗰刻超唔自在 瘋狂吞飯 點知都係勁痛 feel到條刺好似一直插住喉嚨咁 叫埋屋企人幫手用電筒照 都搵唔到條刺<br />\n<br />\n到第二日忍唔到 去睇醫生先知 純粹插損咗喉嚨 條刺原來一早吞咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有諗過係咪我扣喉嘔到整損個喉嚨先會覺得有野係入面，所以諗住第二日睇下點先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喉嚨損就梗係架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我睇完醫生食埋藥都痛成個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以最好都係睇一次醫生啦！"},{"pid":"560a91badaee4428c8cf9215b497330dddffd177","tid":323552,"uid":28862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:50:26.000Z","msg":"細個試過 呑口水即刻勁痛 feel到佢頂住左<br />\n老母叫我咬啖面包一野吞左佢<br />\n冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55f5df28281439fe243dfdd6b3614179c0cd82c","tid":323552,"uid":15457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:51:21.000Z","msg":"之前試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飲左勁多水舌左勁多舊飯都仲feel到有骨卡係度<br />\n跟住頂唔順去左急症<br />\n比左醫生檢查同照埋x光<br />\n乜都check唔到跟住叫我第2日返去照胃鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後第2日起身乜事都無 胃鏡都無去照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b92d722df32c681bee1f667824179f4e230e032","tid":323552,"uid":59550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:52:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無耐前試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n卡住嗰刻超唔自在 瘋狂吞飯 點知都係勁痛 feel到條刺好似一直插住喉嚨咁 叫埋屋企人幫手用電筒照 都搵唔到條刺<br />\n<br />\n到第二日忍唔到 去睇醫生先知 純粹插損咗喉嚨 條刺原來一早吞咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有諗過係咪我扣喉嘔到整損個喉嚨先會覺得有野係入面，所以諗住第二日睇下點先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喉嚨損就梗係架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我睇完醫生食埋藥都痛成個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以最好都係睇一次醫生啦！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好喇"},{"pid":"844474ec19facf20334cf96f165112fa50cfa487","tid":323552,"uid":59550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:53:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飲左勁多水舌左勁多舊飯都仲feel到有骨卡係度<br />\n跟住頂唔順去左急症<br />\n比左醫生檢查同照埋x光<br />\n乜都check唔到跟住叫我第2日返去照胃鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後第2日起身乜事都無 胃鏡都無去照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能一早吞咗落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d70646ab4627804a4d7be3b496886873212888","tid":323552,"uid":59550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:53:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個試過 呑口水即刻勁痛 feel到佢頂住左<br />\n老母叫我咬啖面包一野吞左佢<br />\n冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我依家煮緊飯，希望得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce2da6ce3bafcb7ceafa97740fe7bcd290ee6ac","tid":323552,"uid":59550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:58:02.000Z","msg":"如果吞完飯都唔得我就真係要去睇急症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d26457c02da755aa3eec32b2d8f1237fd884350","tid":323552,"uid":32279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T18:10:11.000Z","msg":"我細個都係咁 好淆底口水都唔敢吞<br />\n然後即刻去急症 我老豆醒<br />\n佢去買支水同蛋糕比我<br />\n叫我試下飲啖水 唔想嘥$100<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知飲完大啖水真係吞左落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw骨落呢個傳聞 讀急救個老師解釋<br />\n其實係自己拎個碗同筷子篤同講骨落<br />\n咁你不自覺向上望集中篤 拉直左個頸定喉嚨<br />\n然後一路講骨落個喉嚨又會郁 就落到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係聽佢講 唔知佢係咪吹水"},{"pid":"58a845367af3f68c54aeadf9676da1de3cdf919d","tid":323552,"uid":29717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T18:11:23.000Z","msg":"細個都係哽過魚骨，從此唔太敢食魚"},{"pid":"c3df8f686c6f78a8a4ff12ab4364fe55bca9e612","tid":323552,"uid":1